==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[lose]] [[the]] [[plot]]'''

# {{idiom}} An inchoative idiom to indicate a person's ceasing to behave in a predictable and/or rational manner and beginning to behave unpredictably and often outrageously.  The allegory is to a character in a play or screenplay whose behaviour suddenly deviates from what the audience would expect.

